{"tid":1235631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭老母千其唔好落台！！！","createTime":"2019-06-17T07:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T19:30:44.000Z","uid":188828,"like":1856,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":158,"replies":[{"pid":"56c6522e279cc1f7a321020a3df06f06af2f7805","tid":1235631,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:47:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭老母千其唔好落台<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">住</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efuxFQR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefuxFQR.png&h=97cdcb3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n眼見大家成日叫佢落台<br />\n甚至Gphone回應記者問題第一句都係叫林奠落台 <br />\n第二句先話撤回惡法<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日冷靜落黎我覺得<br />\n大家唔好再錯重點<br />\n我唔係話佢唔應該落台<br />\n但呢個唔係最有迫切性！！！<br />\n大家唔該幫手推推<br />\n佢落咗台仲有千千萬萬個佢<br />\n佢落台前一定要攪到真普選<br />\n咁樣佢落台先有意思！<br />\n<br />\n各位手足麻煩推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64502bc6ad68f9c2a99e0757fd8071720b6f0e7d","tid":1235631,"uid":188828,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92334c840f2d30c650365a831bb8d0b4021c0797","tid":1235631,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:49:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f22bb52d586b99c43e44417c98129fabddb8af9b","tid":1235631,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92334c840f2d30c650365a831bb8d0b4021c0797","tid":1235631,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:49:12.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:49:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"000acfc21e4698a2b7832a1539529296a409ec5e","tid":1235631,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f22bb52d586b99c43e44417c98129fabddb8af9b","tid":1235631,"uid":5205,"like":0,"disl